Xubuntu desktop seed
====================

----------------------
Task-Per-Derivative: 1
Task-Section: user
Task-Description: Xubuntu desktop
Task-Extended-Description: This task provides the Xubuntu desktop environment.
Task-Key: xubuntu-desktop
Task-Name: xubuntu-desktop
Task-Seeds: desktop-common core
----------------------

## This seed inherits packages from 'core', so will appear to be missing many important packages.

== Network Services ==

Basic network services and Windows integration.

 * (network-manager-pptp)
 * (network-manager-pptp-gnome)

== GUI infrastructure ==

== Extra fonts (should be common, but not so for space reasons) ==
 * (fonts-noto-cjk)
 * (fonts-noto-hinted)
 * (fonts-nanum)
 * (fonts-opensymbol)
 * (fonts-liberation)

== Input methods ==
 * (im-config)

== Desktop Xfce Apps ==

=== Common with Ubuntu ===
 * (apport-gtk)
 * (whoopsie)              # http://wiki.ubuntu.com/ErrorTracker
 * (desktop-file-utils)
 * (file-roller)
 * (gnome-calculator)
 * (gnome-software)
 * (app-install-data-partner)
 * (transmission-gtk)       # simple GNOME frontend for bittorrent downloads
 * (system-config-printer-gnome)
 * (gnome-system-tools)
 * language-selector-gnome	   # MichaelVogt
 * (firefox)
 * (xul-ext-ubufox)        # ubuntu firefox tweaks - AlexanderSack
 * update-manager
 * (update-notifier)
 * zenity
 * (gvfs-fuse)			# let non-GNOME apps see GVFS via fuse
 * (gvfs-backends)      # otherwise no network tab

